Invocation Name: new rock
des:
New Rock is synonymous with bringing you quality music from both signed and independent musicians from around the globe. If you have landed hear then you have stumbled across our voice command Skill for Amazon Alexa linking your voice to the New Rock’s Music Database.

Have you ever heard a song on the radio on wondered “who am I listening to”, well from now on just ask... No really just ask. When you install this skill to your Amazon Alexa account, then your voice becomes your key to all the music knowledge that you could need. If you ask your Amazon Alexa really nicely this Skill will even save you a link to the artist to pick up again later.
